metadata.name: Hidden Star
metadata.description: CosmOwner is the perfect symbiosis between the real and the virtual world. This NFT cards collection represents all the 9095 visible stars officially registered and photographed by satellite. The ranking of each NFT is based on the real properties of each Star. Therefore each NFT represents a unique Star, and the collection is very limited. This number of NFTs can only evolve with science and discoveries ! (https://www.cosmowner.com/)
